{"tid":623920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登d鬥地主撚言論真係好好笑","createTime":"2018-04-10T11:15:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T16:41:00.000Z","uid":35870,"like":16,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"21f122287cace7af607b7369bd0861a36934f232","tid":623920,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T11:15:46.000Z","msg":"講緊以下呢個post:<br />\n<br />\n擁1.5萬個物業　超級業主獲退逾億差餉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入面d comment，真係笑死，成班係到話咩有成萬個物業，嘩，等於兩個屋苑呀！！d霸權真係好pk呀<br />\n<br />\n跟住又話咩，係咪華X地產商？新界d樓可能都有成萬個單位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仆街囤樓霸權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> d樓價唔會跌喇！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇到呢到，真心想笑，究竟平時會上連登嘅係咩人呢？其實我相信都有好多大學生三大撚名校撚上，斷估無理由講埋d咁荒謬嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n喂喂，差餉呢，係包埋商業大廈架，一棟icc一個朗豪坊都唔知去左幾多單位啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有d發展商嘅主要收入來源例如新x基(定新x唔記得)都係黎自property management呢類，即係成棟寫字樓租出去收租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，單一業主有萬幾個單位，根本唔係咩奇怪事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 更加同咩樓價霸權無關"},{"pid":"b7283b72a0ccefe44758cac5167ccc772f659aa1","tid":623920,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T11:18:19.000Z","msg":"禁錯制將條link變左member添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n擁1.5萬個物業　超級業主獲退逾億差餉<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/t/623399/1?ref=android\" target=\